utes\nof observing time without the loss of tiles and probability. Further, we\ndemonstrate that as compared to the greedy algorithm, the airmass-weighted\nalgorithm can acquire up to 20 % more probability and 30 sq. deg. more in areal\ncoverage for skymaps of all sizes and configurations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Feb 2019 06:56:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-15"}
