vations regarding the stability of deterministic fixed\npoints, and the breaking of ergodicity in the large-volume limit.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Feb 2019 09:47:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
